    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fresh, exciting take on the old retro space shooter, born from the love for arcade gaming. Destroiders will keep you on your toes in this fast-paced, space drifter. There is no rest when deciding whether to destroy your mate and steal his resources or mine your own before facing bloodthirsty space monsters and alien ships waiting to crush your puny little dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/98f5350c99d8cbcbfe903080f09294ac.poster.avif?t=1728068329\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/98f5350c99d8cbcbfe903080f09294ac.webm?t=1728068329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/98f5350c99d8cbcbfe903080f09294ac.mp4?t=1728068329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroiders is a 2.5D skill-based Asteroids-inspired shoot ‘em up. Drift around destroying, avoiding and harvesting asteroids. Use your shield to bounce off hurtling obstacles and protect yourself from incoming fire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play either on your own or with your mates in coop/ comp multiplayer. In Coop mode, see how many points you and your teammates can collect before the round ends, or play competitively and humiliate the other teams by reaching the final round with the most points or knocking them out early.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/be4f38898a6a03cffce85a328bede116.poster.avif?t=1728068329\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/be4f38898a6a03cffce85a328bede116.webm?t=1728068329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/be4f38898a6a03cffce85a328bede116.mp4?t=1728068329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 4 players and up to four teams. <strong> Different combinations of controller types may allow for more players</strong>)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choice from a selection of distinct environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single player or cooperative/competitive multiplayer (<strong>Couch Coop Only</strong>)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple drifting game with increasing difficulty with each level </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online and Local Leader board for cooperative mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 types of deadly weapons at your disposal </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect yourself with your shield</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter numerous alien species </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plays well on Steamdeck</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4 Weapon Types at your disposal:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Laser Gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Gatling Gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Mine Deployer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Rocket Launcher</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/db6ba6975f256eef4ecf7ff0f17cea4e.poster.avif?t=1728068329\" width=192 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/db6ba6975f256eef4ecf7ff0f17cea4e.webm?t=1728068329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/db6ba6975f256eef4ecf7ff0f17cea4e.mp4?t=1728068329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4 alien species that will make your life a misery:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Screamer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gobbler</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UFO</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sawer</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/cdfa8c8e5b8fcd743aad7a3294627ff9.poster.avif?t=1728068329\" width=640 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/cdfa8c8e5b8fcd743aad7a3294627ff9.webm?t=1728068329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077580/extras/cdfa8c8e5b8fcd743aad7a3294627ff9.mp4?t=1728068329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEFORE BUYING PLEASE NOTE (NOT SO SMALL PRINT)</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAYING ON A BIG SCREEN RECOMMENDED. THE BIGGER THE BETTER.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THIS IS A COUCH COOP GAME ONLY, TO PLAY ONLINE USE REMOTE PLAY (LINK BELOW).</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MORE PLAYERS EQUALS MORE THINGS REQUIRING MORE COMPUTER POWER.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FIXED CONTROL SCHEME, SORRY. BUT THE ONE IT HAS IS A GOOD ONE.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
